criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. severe uterine adhesion or uterine adhesion with 2 times of uterine cavity surgery with endometrium less than 7mm;
2. thin endometrium less than 7mm even after endometrial preparation;
3. cycle cancelled because of thin endometrium less than 7mm, RIF or RSA with endometrial thickness less than 8mm.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. age >42;
2. combined with other uterine disease like submucous fibroid,endometrial polyp and untreated uterine malformation;
3. combined with serious disease, such as heart diseases, diabetes, hypertensio1ahistory of pelvic surgery.
